Hangzhou Zheben Import And Export Co., Ltd.
Company Overview
HANGZHOU ZHEBEN IMPORT AND EXPORT CO.,LTD. is a professional large-scale manufacturer of all types of weighing scale, integrating development and production together. Our main products include real weighing scale,digital scale,body fat scale,luggage scale,kitchen scale,electronic scale,bathroom scale. Our company was established in 2000, and we have many years of history in the weighing scale industry. Located near NingBo,Hangzhou Airport we enjoy convenient water, land and air transportation. Our company employs more than 200 workers; through the efforts of our entire staff, we have become Amazon,Wal-Mart,IKEA, weighing scale supplier. HANGZHOU ZHEBEN IMPORT AND EXPORT CO.,LTD people have continuously tried to improve product quality, introducing German technology Moreover, We use the best raw materials, giving our company good technical capabilities. Our annual production capability is 3 million sets of electronic scales.Currently, HANGZHOU ZHEBEN IMPORT AND EXPORT CO.,LTD weighing scale is already exported to America, France, Australia, Italy and 20 other countries and regions. Our company has always focused on research, development and innovation, And we have recently developed a series of new products. we attained ISO9001 Quality Management System Certification,CE,ROHS,BSCI,Certification. Our company regards "reasonable prices, efficient production time and good after-sales service" as our tenet. We hope to cooperate with more customers for mutual development and benefits. We welcome potential buyers to contact us.
